ort/">Sport</a></li><li class="section-link"><a href="http://www.thebubble.org.uk/tv/">Television</a></li><li class="section-link"><a href="http://www.thebubble.org.uk/travel/">Travel</a></li><li class="section-link"><a href="http://www.thebubble.org.uk/world-affairs/">World Affairs</a></li></ul></div><div id="footrightbar"><div style="text-align:right;"><a href="http://flipside.thebubble.org.uk/"><img src="http://images.thebubble.org.uk/flipside-logo-small.png?1346360864" width="103" height="30"/></a></div><form action="" id="cse-search-box"><div><input type="hidden" name="cx" value="010473932690279393804:2z3_iz_ct10"/><input type="hidden" name="cof" value="FORID:10"/><input type="hidden" name="ie" value="UTF-8"/><input type="text" name="q" size="24" style="width: 100%;"/><input type="submit" name="sa" value="Search"/></div></form><script type="text/javascript" src="http://www.google.com/cse/brand?form=cse-search-box&amp;lang=en"></script><div class="rsbud rsbox">
